- river:$action:$type:$subtype takes precedence
- more granular control over river
	SUBJECT
		river
			:subject
				::undefined
					or
				::$gender		neutral|male|female
					:$rel			self|friend|other

	ACTION
		river
			:action
				::undefined
					or
				::$action
					::$gender
						:$rel



